message.content: cs.AR, cs.ARCH, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.ET - The paper discusses computer architecture research and its future direction, which falls under the category of cs.AR (Architecture). It also mentions the need to bridge the gap between application and device domains, which could be categorized under cs.ARCH (Architectures for Embedded Systems and Signal Processing). The paper also talks about the need to secure a foundational future for information technology, which could be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper discusses trends and vision in the device and circuit domains, which could be categorized under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.ET (Emerging Technologies).
